Basic Qualifications

* BA/BS degree in Radio/TV/Film, Communications, or equivalent experience required

* Minimum of 4+ years of television experience with producing live shows

* Experience with and proficiency in Adobe Creative Suite design programs such as Photoshop and Premiere

* Familiarity with modern web content management systems (Drupal CMS experience a plus)

